result.name: TamJai SamGor MiXian

reviews.text: Amazing food. My boss always eat here also.

Good taste, mushrooms little hard as it seemed, but a part from that great. If you select one of the soups that are not the clear soups, then be aware they are at least little spicy. You can select the spicy level, but little spicy is for most Europeans already quite spicy in this case.
對比起黃大仙中心店，竹園分店的店員服務態度實在好太多
雞翼價貴卻不大隻，服務尚可，凍檸茶好味，小食雲耳量少。
食品滿意，侍應招呼亦好，可以一試！
